 group can set off a magnetic storm."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Many mysteriously appear when more sunspots dot the sun. They stop TV sets from displaying properly."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Three MAGNEMITE are linked by a strong magnetic force. Earaches will occur if you get too close."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"The MAGNEMITE are united by a magnetism so powerful, it dries all moisture in its vicinity."},{"version":"black","text":"Many mysteriously appear when more sunspots dot the sun. They stop TV sets from displaying properly."},{"version":"white","text":"Many mysteriously appear when more sunspots dot the sun. They stop TV sets from displaying properly."},{"version":"black-2","text":"The stronger electromagnetic waves from the three linked Magnemite are enough to dry out surrounding moisture."},{"version":"white-2","text":"The stronger electromagnetic waves from the three linked Magnemite are enough to dry out surrounding moisture."},{"version":"x","text":"A linked cluster formed of several Magnemite. It discharges powerful magnetic waves at high voltage."},{"version":"y","text":"Generates strange radio signals. It raises the temperature by 3.6 degrees Fahrenheit within 3,300 feet."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Magneton emits a powerful magnetic force that is fatal to mechanical devices. As a result, large cities sound sirens to warn citizens of large-scale outbreaks of this Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Magneton emits a powerful magnetic force that is fatal to electronics and precision instruments. Because of this, it is said that some towns warn people to keep this Pok\u00e9mon inside a Pok\u00e9 Ball."},{"version":"sun","text":"When three Magnemite link together, their brains also become one. They do not become three times more intelligent."},{"version":"moon","text":"It has about three times the electrical power of Magnemite. For some reason, outbreaks of this Pok\u00e9mon happen when lots of sunspots appear."},{